PrecisOrder designating (a) the MINISTER of INDUSTRY for the purposes of this Act and as the Minister in relation to small businesses in Quebec, (b) the MINISTER for the purposes of the ATLANTIC CANADA OPPORTUNITIES AGENCY ACT in relation to small businesses in the four maritime provinces, and (c) the MINISTER OF WESTERN ECONOMIC DIVERSIFICATION in relation to small businesses in the four western provinces.
